{"tid":2134764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【窮能搬屋】90後情侶真人騷 $7000想租329呎凶宅：間屋有股霉味","createTime":"2020-08-01T03:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T04:02:59.000Z","uid":333533,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6973892da53e70edfc5b761ccc548d89d270c2d0","tid":2134764,"uid":333533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"據《2020年國際房價負擔能力》報告，香港樓價連續第十年蟬聯全球最貴，一個入息達中位數的家庭（即平均月入約$28,000），需不吃不喝21年才夠錢上車。上年居屋申請超額認購60.5倍，今年又因疫情，遲遲未公佈申請日期，年輕人買不起私樓，又抽不到居屋，租樓似乎是他們找尋私人空間的最好方法。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的Ray和24歲的Eva拍拖兩年，上年他們用$13,500，在東涌租住了一個408呎的單位同居。原本只是想有更多二人世界的時間，但同居後遇上反送中運動，他們慶幸自己當初選擇搬出來住，「和家人政見不合，如果沒有搬出來住，應該每日都吵架。」一年死約過後，撞正武漢肺炎肆虐，二人被減人工，月入合共$45,000。雖然不算少，但因原業主拒絕減租，二人決定搬走，改租另一個月租$10,000以下的單位，希望儲錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200801/ZPJNV2XA6NC25BOE7TLF4DYGNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200801%2FZPJNV2XA6NC25BOE7TLF4DYGNI%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzObXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=7f76366c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200801%2FZPJNV2XA6NC25BOE7TLF4DYGNI%2F&h=ab7aba55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200801/ZPJNV2XA6NC25BOE7TLF4DYGNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />7000係咪得女神套房揀"},{"pid":"71132ac4e4f55408144daf684339cfddc12cbd32","tid":2134764,"uid":51369,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"月入45k駛唔駛租個7k兇宅呀<br />\n真係做show咩"},{"pid":"cb62b9a695bd6ac9fe2717e70348946bf45f2b74","tid":2134764,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"兇宅未必有鬼，但係兇宅而有霉味都幾肯定有"},{"pid":"8ae65839ee8f7aa7298b247bb11ddaae43d1e15c","tid":2134764,"uid":333533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"71132ac4e4f55408144daf684339cfddc12cbd32","tid":2134764,"uid":51369,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score